Compiled for 32-bit with MinGW. A Code::Blocks project.

Playing around with FreeGLUT to create a simple game engine, used C.


Keys:
W,A,S,D - move
shift+W,shift+S - turn up/down
Q,E - turn left/right
ESC - Quit
F12 - Change keyboard layout recognition between QWERTY and DVORAK

2012/07/27
-I used dvorak keyboard layout, so for easier testing I included a function key to change between the layouts, to get WASD working at the right part of the keyboard
